explains: n. 横梁，横楣；[建] 气窗

sentences.en: The transom condition for speed displacement ships is discussed.
sentences.cn: 讨论了高速排水型船舶的方尾条件。

sentences.en: Transom and cockpit components sorted and being moved to the boat.
sentences.cn: 横梁和驾驶舱部分排序和被转移到小船。

sentences.en: Start by taping the transom with painters tape so you can mark your hardware locations as you go.
sentences.cn: 开始录制的横梁与画家磁带，因此您可以标记您的硬件地点你去。
